## Using Spacing

### Theme Spacing Constants

```dart
// ✅ Correct
SizedBox(height: AppTheme.spacingMd)
Padding(padding: EdgeInsets.all(AppTheme.spacingSm))
SizedBox(width: AppTheme.spacingLg)

// ❌ Wrong - Hardcoded values
SizedBox(height: 16)
Padding(padding: EdgeInsets.all(8))
```

### Available Spacing

| Constant | Value | Usage |
|----------|-------|-------|
| `AppTheme.spacingXs` | 4.0 | Tiny gaps |
| `AppTheme.spacingSm` | 8.0 | Small padding |
| `AppTheme.spacingMd` | 16.0 | Standard padding |
| `AppTheme.spacingLg` | 24.0 | Large sections |
| `AppTheme.spacingXl` | 32.0 | Major sections |

