## Widget Best Practices

### Widget Size

- Keep widgets **under 200 lines**
- **Single responsibility** - one clear purpose
- Extract reusable parts to separate widgets

### Widget Types

| Type | When to Use |
|------|-------------|
| `StatelessWidget` | No internal state needed |
| `StatefulWidget` | Local state only (animations, controllers) |
| `ConsumerWidget` | Accessing Riverpod providers (preferred) |
| `ConsumerStatefulWidget` | Local state + Riverpod |

### Performance

```dart
// ✅ Use const constructors
const SizedBox(height: 16)
const Text('Static text')
const MyWidget()

// ✅ Use ListView.builder for long lists
ListView.builder(
  itemCount: items.length,
  itemBuilder: (context, index) => ItemWidget(items[index]),
)

// ❌ Avoid ListView with children for long lists
ListView(children: items.map((i) => ItemWidget(i)).toList())
```

