## Common UI Patterns

### Container with Theme

```dart
Container(
  padding: EdgeInsets.all(AppTheme.spacingMd),
  decoration: BoxDecoration(
    color: Theme.of(context).colorScheme.surface,
    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(AppTheme.radiusMd),
    border: Border.all(color: AppTheme.borderColor),
  ),
  child: Text(
    'Content',
    style: Theme.of(context).textTheme.bodyLarge,
  ),
)
```

### Card with Theme

```dart
Card(
  color: Theme.of(context).colorScheme.surface,
  elevation: 2,
  shape: RoundedRectangleBorder(
    borderRadius: BorderRadius.circular(AppTheme.radiusMd),
  ),
  child: Padding(
    padding: EdgeInsets.all(AppTheme.spacingMd),
    child: Column(
      crossAxisAlignment: CrossAxisAlignment.start,
      children: [
        Text('Title', style: Theme.of(context).textTheme.titleLarge),
        SizedBox(height: AppTheme.spacingSm),
        Text('Body', style: Theme.of(context).textTheme.bodyLarge),
      ],
    ),
  ),
)
```

### Button with Theme

```dart
ElevatedButton(
  style: ElevatedButton.styleFrom(
    backgroundColor: Theme.of(context).colorScheme.primary,
    foregroundColor: Theme.of(context).colorScheme.onPrimary,
    padding: EdgeInsets.symmetric(
      horizontal: AppTheme.spacingLg,
      vertical: AppTheme.spacingMd,
    ),
  ),
  onPressed: () {},
  child: Text('Button'),
)
```

### ListTile with Theme

```dart
ListTile(
  title: Text(
    'Title',
    style: Theme.of(context).textTheme.titleMedium,
  ),
  subtitle: Text(
    'Subtitle',
    style: Theme.of(context).textTheme.bodyMedium?.copyWith(
      color: Theme.of(context).colorScheme.onSurface.withValues(alpha: 0.6),
    ),
  ),
  leading: Icon(
    Icons.person,
    color: Theme.of(context).colorScheme.primary,
  ),
)
```

### SwitchListTile with Theme

```dart
SwitchListTile(
  title: Text('Enable', style: AppTheme.bodyLarge),
  value: isEnabled,
  onChanged: (value) => setEnabled(value),
  activeTrackColor: AppTheme.primary.withValues(alpha: 0.5),
  thumbColor: WidgetStateProperty.resolveWith((states) {
    if (states.contains(WidgetState.selected)) {
      return AppTheme.primary;
    }
    return null;
  }),
)
```

### Color with Opacity (Modern API)

```dart
// ❌ DEPRECATED - Will cause lint warning
color.withOpacity(0.5)

// ✅ CORRECT - Use withValues
color.withValues(alpha: 0.5)

// Example usage
Container(
  color: AppTheme.primary.withValues(alpha: 0.1),  // 10% opacity
)
BoxShadow(
  color: AppTheme.shadowColor.withValues(alpha: 0.2),  // 20% opacity
)
```

