## Checklist

- [ ] All colors from `AppTheme` or `Theme.of(context).colorScheme`
- [ ] All text styles from `AppTheme` or `Theme.of(context).textTheme`
- [ ] All spacing from `AppTheme.spacing*`
- [ ] No hardcoded `Color(0x...)` or `Colors.xxx`
- [ ] No `TextStyle()` created from scratch
- [ ] `const` constructors where possible
- [ ] `ListView.builder` for long lists
- [ ] Use existing core widgets when applicable
- [ ] **No `.withOpacity()` - use `.withValues(alpha: X)` instead**
- [ ] **No `activeColor:` on switches - use `thumbColor: WidgetStateProperty`**
- [ ] **No `onPopInvoked:` - use `onPopInvokedWithResult:`**
